 <table-wrap-foot class="table-wrap-foot">
  <title class="title">Note</title>
  <fn id="ece34645-note-0001" class="fn">
   <p class="p">If test data are available, binomial probabilities are calculated exactly if the number of test samples is at most 25, otherwise using a normal approximation to the binomial. The “Balance” threshold minimizes 6 × training omission rate +0.04 × cumulative threshold +1.6 × fractional predicted area.</p>
